overview.en: The Loocar is based on the Ethereum with decentrolized and cryptography counting system integrated into rental car block, which aims to be the first car rented blockchain system in the world.
overview.zh: 行车链（LCR）是一款搭建在全球公有链以太坊（Ethereum Blockchain）上的去中心化的移动应用，旨在成为全球共享型汽车租赁平台，即区块链界的嘀嘀打车。
